{"tid":127351,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"街S泊位求心得#adore#","createTime":"2017-02-20T04:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T02:18:01.000Z","uid":76434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9952bcd072f91bc599f7811f0c76313cb881d0b8","tid":127351,"uid":76434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:54:45.000Z","msg":"停車場L泊位好熟 但泊街又多車後面又有人推緊真係唔知點好<br />\n<br />\n學車s泊位冇車同睇雪糕桶好易 但出到街完全唔係個回事 宜家都唔係幾泊得好 成日泊到好出唔貼線<br />\n<br />\n有冇大師可以畀個心得黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c9ae1bc59a93cefc0a0808d8510cf3a819e3295","tid":127351,"uid":33039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:56:06.000Z","msg":"上youtube睇s位教學<br />\n文字形容唔到 其實靠感覺居多"},{"pid":"72087113080fdb2a6af35aa95806b5fab94c5ecb","tid":127351,"uid":59001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T04:57:15.000Z","msg":"通常我都係對正個位之前落車一掌推架車入去"},{"pid":"1525e8d70e808d9bc7782f2976f2f29b5f412c6f","tid":127351,"uid":25319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T05:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>通常我都係對正個位之前落車一掌推架車入去</blockquote><br />\n收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc85f5ee6b0de99939fd40bdb58a95f9e810b71","tid":127351,"uid":71075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T05:33:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2599a9dc007a7ca295bb1bcf59041cc66361665a","tid":127351,"uid":76434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T06:15:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟有啲小心得分享下，當然唔一定100%有效，做個參考試試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以你要泊右邊為例。<br />\n首先要先判斷好你隔離個車位係夠你扭入去先。<br />\n然後響要扭入去果個位隔離，預最少半個車位位置打斜近45度角，車頭向左，屎忽對向車位內。<br />\n留意左鏡見到空位後面架車個右頭燈，要見到晒而岩岩好就夠，直入車位。<br />\n當你入到咁上下，右前方盲區(A柱)同你車位前車尾左尾燈交叉時，將堂軚扭到最左，注意右頭燈唔好成個車埋對方個尾，必要時探個頭出去睇。<br />\n當差唔多部車成個頭對正人地個車尾同時，留意下右邊會唔會上駁/車尾太貼後車車頭，有需要再修正下位置。<br />\n泊左位技巧一樣，只係睇鏡個方法掉轉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟平時都係用呢招，最多兩手到入到晒。多練習就OK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打 好實用 <br />\n即係留足夠距離平排 扭右到45度 -&gt;呢個位要扭盡右軚定扭一圈右就夠？<br />\n直入 -&gt; 回返正堂軚直入<br />\n右前方盲區(A柱)同你車位前車尾左尾燈交叉時，將堂軚扭到最左 -&gt; 扭到最之後入車位<br />\n<br />\n我有冇理解錯？"},{"pid":"87d14b03e2dc6be95f8396ac6813e26067a865e7","tid":127351,"uid":79558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:20:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fjTx0Jtqccw&amp;list=PL8imrieVGziOoJq0D61XRIS0cgmaDGeyx&amp;index=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfjTx0Jtqccw%26list%3DPL8imrieVGziOoJq0D61XRIS0cgmaDGeyx%26index%3D1&d=d%2FCPXFTd5ssE%2Fv2vqbbCu%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=836927e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fjTx0Jtqccw&amp;list=PL8imrieVGziOoJq0D61XRIS0cgmaDGeyx&amp;index=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f57d94a242bf1d8d639cd6a63f8b9439868d979","tid":127351,"uid":71075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:22:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3fc05fd8785e2c8618874bdb4e76da3ba71cc590","tid":127351,"uid":16362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O37YCq8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO37YCq8.jpg&h=5f1f69e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n斜住尾入應該最易"},{"pid":"7d0a35f94573644b84ea764b7e68f3396f474b3d","tid":127351,"uid":71075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:28:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"33c14135bd3f8aaf0ef7e358ff064702cb11ea97","tid":127351,"uid":71075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:29:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9da996feed1f29a38514ecec7abea50d58dde6a","tid":127351,"uid":33022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T08:58:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係果句，工多藝熟，操多幾次就有自己一套方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無撚錯"},{"pid":"6cd4066cf1e16cbc3923b6fbef7c00717cc23627","tid":127351,"uid":81737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"工多"},{"pid":"02f5055784a9c6d940244eb1a56c71f240e372ba","tid":127351,"uid":16362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T09:00:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都係果句，工多藝熟，操多幾次就有自己一套方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢都講佢L位好熟，其實個道理都係一樣，幻想自己點樣出車就倒返轉黎入，夜晚去工業區練多d啦"},{"pid":"71acd528852d66b71b8fc1a9cee53fe7a82b87ae","tid":127351,"uid":16362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T09:07:15.000Z","msg":"再簡單d就係同前車位平排先，隔半米至一米，之後r波，當你見到佢後座車門就扭盡左，慢慢向後，右鏡果到後車左前燈就扭右入，同前車直線後就前後再慢慢adjust"},{"pid":"da893d4200d9c5cf06e7a083270eb85e007b9363","tid":127351,"uid":71075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T10:25:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c3891265b0e2da76cc50ed2d6acf54370d4c683a","tid":127351,"uid":31015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T10:55:33.000Z","msg":"唔好理後面堆車<br />\n陏埋上半身去睇左右鏡<br />\n可以幫你睇到更多角度<br />\n我左鏡會大約睇到左後碌個位<br />\n泊左邊 見仲有一隻半腳掌就回呔喇<br />\n另外 偷位打斜再入係會易d<br />\n<br />\n不過熟能生巧係邊要"},{"pid":"d868e0e90677fa841bd3117d07e3124f7f820b6e","tid":127351,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T11:36:46.000Z","msg":"之前唔記得蘋果定邊份報有教點泊s位<br />\n主要睇a柱 後車鬼面罩同後輪<br />\n初初又係唔識泊s位<br />\n我依家多數都泊到"},{"pid":"280eedcedeafa705b24ee06eac98235b1396dd89","tid":127351,"uid":76434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T12:57:39.000Z","msg":"多謝咁多位巴打 好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問多句<br />\n例如去到旺角想泊街 條街泊滿晒得返一個位 我又要向前同前車平排 我點樣signal我後面架車 同佢講&quot;我準備泊呢個位 你唔好駛上黎塞住我&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aceade99d622e63c29655029cbe975fbeb3c6818","tid":127351,"uid":6016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T13:00:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝咁多位巴打 好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問多句<br />\n例如去到旺角想泊街 條街泊滿晒得返一個位 我又要向前同前車平排 我點樣signal我後面架車 同佢講&quot;我準備泊呢個位 你唔好駛上黎塞住我&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早幾個車位好打定左燈收慢車速"},{"pid":"afda534f87f0b8ea631048de0452971d1e3f66c3","tid":127351,"uid":71075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:41:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a905382997a0eab2a6891504cf10b1c830cce966","tid":127351,"uid":16362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T20:58:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>多謝咁多位巴打 好有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問多句<br />\n例如去到旺角想泊街 條街泊滿晒得返一個位 我又要向前同前車平排 我點樣signal我後面架車 同佢講&quot;我準備泊呢個位 你唔好駛上黎塞住我&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n早少少打死火燈同慢車"},{"pid":"e26487d29afbc6d74c0b677c631c12c4c34fc30b","tid":127351,"uid":16362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T20:58:39.000Z","msg":"如果係search緊位既話就一直打死火燈話比人知收油"},{"pid":"bc33ae922a90cf07e63aab6b91d7443df57ca9b7","tid":127351,"uid":629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T01:39:02.000Z","msg":"根據上面條片<br />\n同前車車平排 相隔50-100cm 扭盡左<br />\n當右鏡見到後車成個車頭 直軚<br />\n當右後輪掂拍車線 扭盡右"},{"pid":"7863b51ecf351234c62b0731ac9a5aeef72c25de","tid":127351,"uid":38946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T01:51:28.000Z","msg":"45度入 斜入唔到就貼埋些小前車再入 都係操得多熟架車"}]}